data.description: Much more to offer other than a large 4 bedroom home. In addition to the attached 2 car garage with large storage room there is an additional 2 car detached garage with half bath and one bedroom one bath apartment upstairs. Another 28x40 shop with half bath. RV storage pad with both 50 amp and 30 amp hookup and septic/water hookup. Inside, the home offers rooms for any use or hobby one might need. A large living room, separate den, formal living room or dinning room, 4th bedroom is large enough to use as a Game Room. Everything here plus a fantastic location in very low traffic area. 2023-07-30
